#. module: bowling
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bowling.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Customers are hungry? Allow them to purchase drinks, snacks and a bite "
"through the <strong>Point of Sale app</strong>"
msgstr ""
"So stranke lačne? Omogočite jim nakup pijače, prigrizkov in prigrizkov preko "
"<strong>Aplikacije za Prodajno mesto</strong>"

#. module: bowling
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bowling.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Customers can also rent bowling shoes - keep an eye on which lanes are "
"supposed to return how many shoes at a glance using the Point of Sale order "
"overviews."
msgstr ""
"Stranke si lahko izposodijo tudi bowling čevlje – s pregledi naročil na "
"prodajnem mestu lahko na hitro preverite, katere steze naj bi vrnile koliko "
"čevljev."

#. module: bowling
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bowling.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Customers can book a session using the <strong>Appointments app's page </"
"strong>on your website, and pay in just a few clicks"
msgstr ""
"Stranke lahko rezervirajo termin na strani <strong>aplikacije Termini </"
"strong>na vašem spletnem mestu in plačajo z le nekaj kliki."

#. module: bowling
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bowling.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Customers hungry, or need to book a lane on the spot? Just use the Point of "
"Sale app to manage food sales, and attribute them to the correct bowling "
"lanes to keep an easy overview of what goes where."
msgstr ""
"Ste stranke lačne ali morate takoj rezervirati stezo? Preprosto uporabite "
"aplikacijo Point of Sale za upravljanje prodaje hrane in jo dodelite "
"pravilnim stezam za kegljanje, da boste imeli enostaven pregled nad tem, kaj "
"kam gre."

#. module: bowling
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bowling.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Customize your appointment reminders to tailor them to your company's "
"branding"
msgstr ""
"Prilagodite opomnike za sestanke, da bodo ustrezali blagovni znamki vašega "
"podjetja"

